    <item>
      <title>雷帕霉素或可延缓衰老。以下是该药物的测试方法</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/07/01/nx-s1-5008777/rapamycin-aging-disease-drug-humans-research</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长寿研究人员正在服用一种他们认为可能有助于延长人们寿命的仿制药。现在，一位牙医正在测试雷帕霉素是否能阻止牙龈疾病——这是与年龄有关的疾病的“煤矿中的金丝雀”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/07/01/nx-s1-5008777/rapamycin-aging-disease-drug-humans-research</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
